{"tid":1338834,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"安全返元朗攻略","createTime":"2019-07-21T14:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T14:48:04.000Z","uid":115613,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fc3a3e356bb45c922bd23b72a9f1cc2b06468c02","tid":1338834,"uid":115613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:42:22.000Z","msg":"記得巴絲換白衫之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟有以下攻略返元朗<br />\n<br />\n1）港鐵由屯門避過雞地返元朗攻略：<br />\n<br />\n兆康站<br />\n步行10分鐘至富泰邨對面巴士站坐紅Van （可達元朗廣場、教育路、總站匯豐）<br />\n步行10分鐘至富泰邨對面巴士站坐九巴53（可達大馬路沿途）<br />\n仲可以輕鐵搭一個站去藍地轉紅van，唔駛行咁遠去富泰。<br />\n<br />\n2）天水圍轉輕鐵都可以返元朗。<br />\n<br />\n3）的士<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申： 新界大西北人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a22a5ac2f83fa1bf4844e24181ea6f2a4b3d088","tid":1338834,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc3a3e356bb45c922bd23b72a9f1cc2b06468c02","tid":1338834,"uid":115613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:42:22.000Z","msg":"記得巴絲換白衫之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟有以下攻略返元朗<br />\n<br />\n1）港鐵由屯門避過雞地返元朗攻略：<br />\n<br />\n兆康站<br />\n步行10分鐘至富泰邨對面巴士站坐紅Van （可達元朗廣場、教育路、總站匯豐）<br />\n步行10分鐘至富泰邨對面巴士站坐九巴53（可達大馬路沿途）<br />\n仲可以輕鐵搭一個站去藍地轉紅van，唔駛行咁遠去富泰。<br />\n<br />\n2）天水圍轉輕鐵都可以返元朗。<br />\n<br />\n3）的士<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申： 新界大西北人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:43:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">依家根本點返都唔